{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_136","type":"agent_message","text":"The last issue is task ordering, not behavior: `nativeTest` pulls in the JVM `test` task, and Gradle is currently generating the CGLIB classes before that JVM phase starts. I’m forcing the CGLIB generation task to run after `test` whenever both are in the task graph, so the JVM test uses dynamic CGLIB and the native build still gets the pre-generated classes."}}
